---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Ubicación — Carlos y Marlene"
  description="Toda la información sobre el lugar de la ceremonia y recepción de la boda de Carlos y Marlene."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Ubicación</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Te esperamos en un lugar lleno de encanto y magia.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Venue cards -->
      <div class="venue-grid">
        <!-- Ceremony -->
        <article class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-icon" aria-hidden="true">⛪</div>
          <h2 class="venue-type">Ceremonia</h2>
          <h3 class="venue-name">Capilla San Rafael</h3>
          <address class="venue-address">
            Av. de los Jardines 45<br />
            Col. Las Flores, Ciudad de México<br />
            CP 06700
          </address>
          <dl class="venue-details">
            <div>
              <dt>Fecha</dt>
              <dd>Por confirmar</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>Hora</dt>
              <dd>5:00 pm</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </article>

        <!-- Reception -->
        <article class="venue-card">
          <div class="venue-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌹</div>
          <h2 class="venue-type">Recepción</h2>
          <h3 class="venue-name">Hacienda Las Rosas</h3>
          <address class="venue-address">
            Camino Real de las Rosas 12<br />
            Pedregal Norte, Ciudad de México<br />
            CP 14010
          </address>
          <dl class="venue-details">
            <div>
              <dt>Fecha</dt>
              <dd>Por confirmar</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>Hora</dt>
              <dd>7:30 pm</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Map -->
      <div class="map-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">¿Cómo llegar?</h2>
        <span class="section-divider"></span>

        <div class="map-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Mapa del lugar del evento">
          <span class="map-icon">🗺️</span>
          <p>El mapa interactivo estará disponible próximamente.</p>
          <a
            href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Hacienda+Las+Rosas+Ciudad+de+Mexico"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-primary"
          >
            Abrir en Google Maps
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Real map embed — uncomment and replace src once venue is confirmed -->
        <!--
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=..."
          width="100%"
          height="400"
          style="border:0; border-radius:4px;"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="Ubicación de Hacienda Las Rosas"
        ></iframe>
        -->
      </div>

      <!-- Tips -->
      <div class="tips-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Información adicional</h2>
        <span class="section-divider"></span>
        <ul class="tips-list">
          <li>🚗 Hay estacionamiento gratuito disponible para todos los invitados.</li>
          <li>🏨 Hemos negociado tarifas especiales en el Hotel Las Magnolias (a 5 min del venue). Menciona "Boda Carlos y Marlene" al reservar.</li>
          <li>👗 Código de vestimenta: formal / etiqueta.</li>
          <li>📱 Para cualquier duda, escríbenos a <a href="mailto:hola@carlosymarlene.com">hola@carlosymarlene.com</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--color-blush) 0%, var(--color-cream) 100%);
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* Venue grid */
  .venue-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .venue-card {
    background: var(--color-light);
    border: 1px solid #e8d8c4;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(61, 43, 31, 0.07);
  }

  .venue-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

  .venue-type {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .venue-name {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .venue-address {
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6b5040;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .venue-details {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8d8c4;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .venue-details dt {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .venue-details dd {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  /* Map */
  .map-section { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .map-placeholder {
    background: var(--color-blush);
    border: 2px dashed var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 6px;
    min-height: 300px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .map-icon { font-size: 3.5rem; }

  .map-placeholder p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-light);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.25s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* Tips */
  .tips-section {}

  .tips-list {
    list-style: none;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tips-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-light);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(61, 43, 31, 0.06);
  }
</style>
